# Accessibility & Modding Hooks (2025-06-04)

## Accessibility
- Configurable visual/audio effects for all reality warping and Universal Magic actions
- Options for colorblindness, photosensitivity, and sound sensitivity
- In-game settings for effect intensity, style, and UI scale

## Modding
- APIs/hooks for custom anchor types, effects, and Universal Language puzzles
- Support for community-created anchor sharing, UI themes, and lore extensions
